{"type":"message","id":"290cd8e6","parentId":"fd0cd6ef","timestamp":"2026-04-10T15:35:17.070Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user started a new session. I need to run my startup sequence - reading required files before responding. Let me check what I need to read.\n\nAccording to my instructions, I should read:\n1. MEMORY.md - already in project context\n2. Check for BOOTSTRAP.md - it says [MISSING]\n3. Other relevant files\n\nLooking at my project context, MEMORY.md is already loaded. Let me also check if there are any other startup things I need to do.\n\nFrom MEMORY.md, I see:\n- 最后更新：2026-04-04\n- 关于小八的事实\n- 核心规则\n\nSince this is a new session startup, I should greet the user. I'm configured with the default model being volcengine-plan/doubao-seed-2.0-pro but runtime model is codingplan/minimax-m2.5.\n\nLet me greet the user in a natural way, keeping it brief.\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n你好小八 🦐\n\n新会话已就绪。当前使用 codingplan/minimax-m2.5 模型（默认: volcengine-plan/doubao-seed-2.0-pro）。\n\n今晚想做什么？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":17599,"output":236,"cacheRead":1152,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":18987,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775835287237,"responseId":"019d7807750bfa5d712672e3e488629f"}}
