{"type":"message","id":"21d90f49","parentId":"69bc15c7","timestamp":"2026-04-10T15:41:04.400Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"This is a heartbeat poll. Let me check HEARTBEAT.md as instructed.\n\nLooking at HEARTBEAT.md from the project context provided:\n\n# Heartbeat Configuration\n\n## 心跳规则\n\n### 任务进度上报格式\n```\n[PROGRESS] <percent>% | <step>/<total> | <description>\n```\n\n### 心跳间隔\n- 默认: 30秒\n- 最小: 10秒\n- 最大: 300秒\n\n### 超时处理\n| 情况 | 处理 |\n|------|------|\n| 30秒无输出 | 发送\"仍在运行\"提示 |\n| 60秒无产出 | 警告用户 |\n| 超时前5秒 | 发送即将超时警告 |\n\n### 环境变量\n- `SUBAGENT_MEMORY_LIMIT_MB`: 子代理内存限制 (默认 2048)\n- `PROGRESS_MIN_INTERVAL_MS`: 进度上报最小间隔 (默认 1000)\n\n### 注意事项\n- 长时间任务需定期输出进度\n- 关键里程碑应立即上报\n- 错误信息立即上报，不等待心跳\n\nI just started a new session - there are no ongoing tasks that need attention. I should reply HEARTBEAT_OK.\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\nHEARTBEAT_OK"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":14416,"output":255,"cacheRead":1408,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":16079,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775835642349,"responseId":"019d780ce3194d33599cba252738109c"}}
