{"type":"message","id":"7766113d","parentId":"0a47cfbc","timestamp":"2026-04-10T16:02:16.764Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_79db242ae98b461586c04fb9","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# OpenClaw Self-Improving Memory\n\n## 核心规则\n- 评分后必须等待用户确认才能执行\n- 用户说\"全自动\"或\"直接执行\"时跳过确认\n- 每次纠正立即写入 corrections.md\n- 学到新东西立即写入 ~/self-improving/\n\n## 技能系统\n- v7.0 task-orchestrator (15个模块)\n- auto_improve (6个模块)\n- 意图判断 intent_detector\n- 上下文保护 context_server (18790)\n- Router 反向代理 (3002)\n\n## 用户偏好\n- 深色主题\n- 直接沟通，不拐弯抹角\n\n## 待学习领域\n- WebSocket 对话拦截\n- LLM 集成用于 auto_improve\n\n最后更新: 2026-04-05\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1775836936753}}
{"type":"message","id":"20770f52","parentId":"7766113d","timestamp":"2026-04-10T16:02:16.778Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_a4ea94f7ff1e402b9f1fefcc","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# Corrections Log — Template\n\n> This file is created in `~/self-improving/corrections.md` when you first use the skill.\n> Keeps the last 50 corrections. Older entries are evaluated for promotion or archived.\n\n## Example Entries\n\n```markdown\n## 2026-02-19\n\n### 14:32 — Code style\n- **Correction:** \"Use 2-space indentation, not 4\"\n- **Context:** Editing TypeScript file\n- **Count:** 1 (first occurrence)\n\n### 16:15 — Communication\n- **Correction:** \"Don't start responses with 'Great question!'\"\n- **Context:** Chat response\n- **Count:** 3 → **PROMOTED to memory.md**\n\n## 2026-02-18\n\n### 09:00 — Project: website\n- **Correction:** \"For this project, always use Tailwind\"\n- **Context:** CSS discussion\n- **Action:** Added to projects/website.md\n```\n\n## Log Format\n\nEach entry includes:\n- **Timestamp** — When the correction happened\n- **Correction** — What the user said\n- **Context** — What triggered it\n- **Count** — How many times (for promotion tracking)\n- **Action** — Where it was stored (if promoted)\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1775836936764}}
