{"type":"message","id":"6a86ef22","parentId":"b8a0e565","timestamp":"2026-04-10T16:42:39.169Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户问 second-brain 有什么用，但我没安装这个 skill。我需要解释一下但不需要读取更多内容，因为我没有这个 skill 的信息。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n`second-brain` 是一个流行的个人知识管理系统，通常用于：\n\n- **双向链接笔记**：像 Obsidian 那样笔记之间互相链接\n- **渐进式写作**：从碎片想法构建完整内容\n- **知识图谱**：可视化笔记之间的关系\n- **PARA 方法**：按项目、资源、归档组织信息\n\n如果想用，可以在 ClawHub 搜索安装：\n\n```\nclawhub search second-brain\n```\n\n要我帮你搜一下？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":23223,"output":118,"cacheRead":1152,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":24493,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775839347439,"responseId":"019d7845561f3b090d666bff20ae78f3"}}
